# Dynamic Asset Generator

&nbsp;

***Does nothing on its own***

&nbsp;

A library mod for dynamically generating assets, such as textures, at runtime.

&nbsp;

Note: if world or game loading times are slow, try turning on asset and/or data caching in the config.

**Summary:**

This mod makes chickens, cows, pigs, rabbits, sheep, and villagers fight back!
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
**Donate:**

This is completely optional but if you'd like to support me and my work you can donate to any of the following below:

